title: Match History
body: When I try to view the detailed information on a match, I am unable to except in the post-game lobby. When I click "view details" in my profile under match history, it doesn't work. Same thing happens when I try to get there from the boards.

replies.body: Can you [provide me with a screenshot](https://gyazo.com/) of what you see when this happens?

Thanks for providing that screenshot!

This is part of a known bug with the Match History section of our site. Sometimes this can be resolved by using another browser or by [clearing your browser's cache](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies).

Let me know if you have any questions.
Ah, okay. Thanks for the help!
